OL,3,CFormer world snooker champion Terry
OL,4,CGriffiths dies aged 77
OL,6,FFormer world snooker champion Terry
OL,7,FGriffiths has died aged 77 after a
OL,8,Flong battle with dementia, his family
OL,9,Fhas confirmed.
OL,11,FGriffiths, from south Wales, came
OL,12,Fthrough the qualifying rounds to win
OL,13,Fthe 1979 Crucible title as a
OL,14,Fqualifier, and also won the Masters
OL,15,Fand the UK Championship to complete
OL,16,Fthe sport's illustrious 'triple crown'.
OL,18,FIn later years, Griffiths became an
OL,19,Faccomplished coach, inspiring the
OL,20,Flikes of Stephen Hendry, Mark Williams
OL,21,Fand Mark Allen.
