OL,3,CFormer world snooker champion Terry
OL,4,CGriffiths dies aged 77
OL,6,FThree-time world champion Williams was
OL,7,Famong the first to pay tribute on
OL,8,Fsocial media, describing Griffiths as
OL,9,Fa "mentor, coach, friend, legend".
OL,11,FAllen added: "What a legend of a man
OL,12,Fwho helped shape my career and life
OL,13,Fboth on and off the table. Absolutely
OL,14,Fheartbroken. He wasn't just a coach,
OL,15,Fhe was family."
OL,17,FGriffiths' son Wayne wrote on
OL,18,FFacebook: "To our friends and snooker
OL,19,Ffollowers in general, we are deeply
OL,20,Fsaddened to share the news of our loss.
