OL,6,F"Terry Griffiths OBE passed away
OL,7,Fpeacefully on 1st December, after a
OL,8,Flengthy battle with dementia. He was
OL,9,Fsurrounded by his family in his
OL,10,Fbeloved home-town in South Wales.
OL,12,F"A proud Welshman, Terry was born in
OL,13,FLlanelli, brought pride to Llanelli
OL,14,Fand now he has found peace in
OL,15,FLlanelli. He would not have had it any
OL,16,Fother way."
