OL,3,CFormer world snooker champion Terry
OL,4,CGriffiths dies aged 77
OL,6,FGriffiths was a fixture at the top end
OL,7,Fof the sport during the 1980s and
OL,8,Fearly 1990s, reaching at least the
OL,9,Fquarter-finals of the World
OL,10,FChampionship for nine straight years,
OL,11,Fand reaching the final again in 1988.
OL,13,FHe retired from playing after a first
OL,14,Fround defeat to Williams at the 1997
OL,15,FWorld Championship.
OL,17,FFormer world champion Shaun Murphy
OL,18,Fsaid on X: "Just hearing the news that
OL,19,FTerry Griffiths has passed away. My
OL,20,Fdeepest condolences to his family and
OL,21,Floved ones."
