OL,4,CGriffiths dies aged 77
OL,6,FWorld Snooker posted a statement
OL,7,Fdescribing Griffiths as an "all-time
OL,8,Fsnooker great", adding: "Our sincere
OL,9,Fcondolences to Terry's family and many
OL,10,Ffriends. He was loved and respected by
OL,11,Feveryone in the sport."
OL,13,FThe Welsh Billiards and Snooker
OL,14,FAssociation said: "We are deeply
OL,15,Fsaddened to announce the passing of
OL,16,FWBSA President Terry Griffiths OBE. We
OL,17,Fsend our deepest condolences to
OL,18,FTerry's family."
